 two decades have allowed us all to testify in Chris not just a competent and generous

12
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:22,240
 leadership within the parameter of the evangelical Langham family, but also a biblical and missional

13
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:34,680
 impact on the global Lausanne movement, grounded by a sustained and focused effort in research

14
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:44,160
 and writing for the English-speaking churches worldwide and beyond.

15
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:55,660
 I think you would now agree with me that John Stott had indeed found the impossible candidate

16
00:02:55,660 --> 00:03:06,000
 to accomplish a mission impossible after all. My presence here this evening is to conduct

17
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:14,400
 a dialogue with our distinguished speaker on the topic of the final lecture, the Old

18
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:23,840
 Testament and Christian Hope. Now, I shall assume that a dialogue is opposite to a monologue

